events.name: 話しかける並列/自動実行

parameters:
Miner Fulgor: I am the supervisor here. Is there something
you need?

Clea: I came as a messenger from the Magic Academy's Doctor
Saan.

Miner Fulgor: Oh, that would be helpful! I want to resolve
the incident here secretly.
Clea: May I ask for more details?

Miner Fulgor: Ah, recently the miners here have been
getting attacked.

Miner Fulgor: According to the witnesses, they say it's a
human-like creature.
Clea: Do you have any idea of the whereabouts?
Miner Fulgor: I believe it is the Lefgaria Forest.

Miner Fulgor: If you can resolve this safely, I will show
my gratitude. Please, I beg you!
Miner Fulgor: Oh, so how was it?

Clea: We defeated the beastmen. This is the proof, their
fur.
Miner Fulgor: Haha, please take this ore!

Miner Fulgor: However, please keep it a secret that you
received this from me, okay?
Clea: I came to collect Frimata-san's debt.

Brawler Poson: So that coward finally resorted to asking
someone for help, huh? Well, if there's something I can take
from him, I'll definitely snatch it away!

Clea: I dislike clever tricks. I will defeat you with my
own skills.

Brawler Poson: Even if you're a woman, don't let your guard
down... Fine, I'll repay Frimata the money.

Brawler Poson: I like you. I'll teach you the essence of
violence.
Brawler Poson: Hahaha, you did well for a woman!
Brawler Poson: So, what are you going to do?
Priestess Sophia: How about we cover the expenses?

Brawler Poson: Haha, that's right. I hesitate to hit women
the most!

Clea: Unfortunately, I don't have the money to cover the
expenses.

Brawler Poson: A request for a fight, huh? Hahaha, if you
pay me enough, I'll punch anyone for you.

parameters:
Miner Man: This is a low-grade mine even in Oros. After
all, it's a place where crystals can hardly be obtained.

Miner Man: This is a low-grade mine even in Oros. After

Miner Man: Have you talked to Fulgor? He seems to have

Miner Man: Have you talked to Fulgor? He seems to have

Miner Man: I used to work at the Crystal Mine, but compared

Miner Man: I used to work at the Crystal Mine, but compared

Male Miner: I'm tired of just digging holes all the time.

Miner Man: What's this? Are you gonna treat me to a drink?
It's easy to work when there are only kind people like you
around.

Miner Man: May good fortune be with someone as kind as
you.

Miner Man: The air here is bad. It's better not to stay
here for too long, you know?
Will you have a duel with the apprentice swordsman, Auto?
Apprentice swordsman Auto: I'm sorry for causing trouble.
Clea: I'm ready. Please take care of me.

Apprentice swordsman Auto: Y-You too, please take care of
me!
クレアの決闘戦闘あり

Mercenary Captain Gale: You understand Auto's weakness,
right?

Clea: You have enough physical strength and technique, but
I felt like you lacked confidence.

Clea: Because of that, you haven't been able to fully
utilize your strengths.

Priestess Sophia: Healing is complete. It was the right
decision to have a shield.

Thief Nora: U-Um... It seemed like I was using the shield
to escape.

Mage Relm: I understand being afraid of your own talent!
But overcoming that is the destiny of those with talent!

Mage Relm: W-What is it!? If you have something to say,
please say it!

Apprentice swordsman Auto: You wouldn't understand the
feelings of someone who lacks confidence.

Apprentice swordsman Auto: I thought I could change if I
became a mercenary, but I'm still a coward... I'm still the
same weak-hearted person.

Clea: I am also a cowardly person. There have been times
when I was scared and ran away from the enemy in front of
me.

Clea: Please come with me to the Pizuma Arena. I want you
to see me fight and feel something.

Mercenary Captain Gale: I'll leave the method up to you
guys.

Clea: Thank you very much. Let's meet up at the Pizuma
Arena.

Make sure to win for the sake of our training.

Mercenary Captain Gale: Please assess Auto's actual
abilities.
